sky.f1.uk.title: F1 2025: The Story So Far
sky.f1.uk.description: A McLaren one-two forms the front row for the Australian Grand Prix, as Lando Norris leads from Oscar Piastri. Max Verstappen starts third, while Lewis Hamilton begins from P8. (16.03)

sky.f1.uk.title: F1 2025: The Story So Far
sky.f1.uk.description: It's a first Grand Prix pole for Oscar Piastri as George Russell splits the McLarens with Lando Norris starting third. Sprint winner Lewis Hamilton comes from fifth on the grid. (23.03)

sky.f1.uk.title: F1 2025: The Story So Far
sky.f1.uk.description: It's lights out at Suzuka for the Japanese Grand Prix. World champion Max Verstappen starts from the front of the grid with the McLaren duo of Lando Norris and Oscar Piastri behind. (06.04)

sky.f1.uk.title: F1 2025: The Story So Far
sky.f1.uk.description: It's lights out for the 2025 Bahrain Grand Prix. Oscar Piastri holds pole position with his McLaren teammate Lando Norris down in P6. Charles Leclerc joins Piastri on the front row. (13.04)

sky.f1.uk.title: F1 2025: The Story So Far
sky.f1.uk.description: It's lights out in Jeddah for the 2025 Saudi Arabian Grand Prix. Reigning world champion Max Verstappen crossed the finish line in P1 last season at the Jeddah Corniche Circuit. (20.04)

sky.f1.uk.title: F1 2025: The Story So Far
sky.f1.uk.description: Polesitter Max Verstappen is joined by Lando Norris and Kimi Antonelli heading into turn one, while Lewis Hamilton tries to fight through the field from P12. (04.05)

sky.f1.uk.title: F1 2025: The Story So Far
sky.f1.uk.description: It's lights out at Imola for the 2025 Emilia Romagna Grand Prix. Last season, reigning world champion Max Verstappen held off a late Lando Norris charge to claim race victory. (18.05)

sky.f1.uk.title: F1 2025: The Story So Far
sky.f1.uk.description: On the streets of Monte Carlo, the 2025 Monaco Grand Prix arrives. Lando Norris lines up in P1 with Charles Leclerc behind him as the Monegasque pursues back-to-back home wins. (25.05)

sky.f1.uk.title: F1 2025: The Story So Far

sky.f1.uk.title: F1 2025: The Story So Far

Blaze.uk.title: Storage Hunters

Blaze.uk.title: Storage Wars
Blaze.uk.description: It's a Safe Time to Get Lit!: Kenny rides a recent string of luck right into his unit, while Rene puts his bankroll up against a pair of safes. (S14, ep 16)

Blaze.uk.title: UFO Files
Blaze.uk.description: Alien Engineering (Part 2 of 2): Laser weapons and tele-transporters would probably all be fitted to an alien spaceship, but what if they could be used by humans too? (S1, ep 15)

Blaze.uk.description: Pawn With The Wind: The guys are thrilled when a $1 bill signed by Clark Gable arrives. An item from Ulysses S. Grant's funeral also finds its way into Rick's hands. (S8, ep 21)

Blaze.uk.title: Pawn Stars

Blaze.uk.title: Dickinson's Real Deal

Blaze.uk.title: New: Mysteries From Above

Blaze.uk.title: Paranormal: Caught On Camera

Blaze.uk.title: The UnXplained: of the Universe

Blaze.uk.title: Paranormal Survivor

Blaze.uk.title: UFO Files

Blaze.uk.title: Storage Wars Texas

Blaze.uk.title: Pawn Stars

Blaze.uk.title: Pawn Stars
Blaze.uk.description: James Gang Rides Again: The Pawn Stars are presented with original photographs of Old West outlaw Jesse James and a Leslie organ speaker from the 1950s. (S8, ep 17)

Blaze.uk.title: Pawn Stars
Blaze.uk.description: Wild Thing: The guys check out a fighter plane flown in WWII. Plus, nostalgia strikes Rick when a 1974 VW Thing cruises by. Will his feelings affect his negotiating skills? (S8, ep 18)

Blaze.uk.title: Pawn Stars
Blaze.uk.description: Zoodoo: The guys question the value of a can of joke elephant manure and check out some signed presidential memoirs and a robot toy from the movie Forbidden Planet. (S8, ep 19)

Blaze.uk.title: River Hunters

Blaze.uk.title: River Hunters
Blaze.uk.description: Canterbury Murder: The River Hunters head to Canterbury, where they're granted special permission to undertake the first official search of this section of the River Stour. (S2, ep 4)

Blaze.uk.title: Egypt's Unexplained Files

E4Plus1.uk.description: Sal's Pizza: When Peralta's favourite restaurant burns down, the fire marshal assumes that the owner is the prime suspect. A virus hits the precinct's computers. (S1 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Love Is a Many-Splintered Thing: Bart's heartstrings are pulled once again when Mary Spuckler returns to Springfield, but he doesn't pay her enough attention. (S24 Ep12/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Hardly Kirk-ing: Bart and Milhouse explore the perks of adulthood when a hair-shaving experiment leaves Milhouse looking exactly like his dad Kirk. (S24 Ep13/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK: Reunion
E4Plus1.uk.description: Reunion: Brand new series - It's the reunion dinner party and in true MAFS style, across-the-table action is served as two brides clash. And one groom faces a reckoning! (S10 Ep35)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip from Rude Tube's naughty little sister that features a variety of cats doing strange things, some soldiers stuck in the sand and a dog balancing on a rope.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Selma's Choice: After Homer gets sick from a giant sandwich he's been eating for months, Selma steps in to take the kids to a new alcohol-based theme park. (S4 Ep13/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brother from the Same Planet: When Homer is late picking up Bart from a school football game, Bart gets a surrogate dad from an agency. (S4 Ep14/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sky Police: Chief Wiggum uses a military jet pack to fight crime. But when he crashes into the church, Marge and the congregation resort to gambling to pay for the repairs. (S26 Ep16/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Come Dine with Me: Teens
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Alex goes all-out by making absolutely everything from scratch. Will the fruits of his labour pay off with his dessert, or will he crumble under the pressure? (Ep5/5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: America's Next Top Model
E4Plus1.uk.description: Kyle Hagler: The models are in Milan for meetings with four fashion houses, including Versace. And the contestants are painted like statues for a shoot on Lake Como. (S15 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Reunion: Brand new series - In the reunion Commitment Ceremony, some couples celebrate their journeys, others confront their issues, and one final admission rocks the group. (S10 Ep36)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: MAFS UK: It's Official!
E4Plus1.uk.description: With Lucinda Light: Brand new series - Lucinda dissects all the drama and finds out what her guests Bimini, Davide and Mel really think about the biggest MAFS UK 2025 moments!

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Inbetweeners 2
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2014) Comedy sequel. The lads visit Jay in Australia after he tells them he's living a life of hedonism and sexual promiscuity as a superstar DJ.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK: Reunion
E4Plus1.uk.description: Reunion: Brand new series - In the reunion Commitment Ceremony, some couples celebrate their journeys, others confront their issues, and one final admission rocks the group. (S10 Ep36) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Come Dine with Me: Teens
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Alex goes all-out by making absolutely everything from scratch. Will the fruits of his labour pay off with his dessert, or will he crumble under the pressure? (Ep5/5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Gone Abie Gone: Grampa goes missing. Can Homer and Marge find him by following clues from when he used to work in a restaurant? (S24 Ep4/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Kids These Days: Haley needs motherly advice as she considers her future with Dylan and her career. Jay and Cam's politically incorrect coaching earns them a sensitivity lesson. (S10 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Sketchy Area: Phil finds a new career after visiting Luke's college. Mitch's new case as an assistant DA is marred by an unflattering courtroom sketch by the resident artist. (S10 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Bath Item Gift Hypothesis: At Christmas, Leonard's hunky colleague starts dating Penny, while Sheldon's obsession with gift-giving etiquette torments everyone. (S2 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Killer Robot Instability: Kripke challenges the boys to a robot duel, while Howard is devastated when Penny finally tells him what she thinks of his chauvinism. (S2 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Friendship Algorithm: Sheldon develops a scientific procedure for making friends when he discovers that Kripke has control of a new supercomputer at the university. (S2 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Downtown Boys: To avoid spending Spring Break with his mum, Adam housesits Erica's downtown apartment. Barry and the JTP hope to become a boyband sensation. (S9 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Strangest Affair of All Time: When Murray goes out of town, Jane Bales attempts to make a power grab at the Ottoman Empire, forcing Beverly to retaliate. (S9 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: School-Ercise: As Beverly steps in to teach gym class at William Penn, Barry and Geoff compete for a prized summer internship. (S9 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Grand Theft Scooter: Beverly discovers a big secret in Florida. Erica's heroism overshadows Barry's exam results. (S9 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sunday Chow-Fun Day: With Adam's graduation approaching, Beverly faces a decision: should she stay on as the school's Quaker Warden? (S9 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Made in Chelsea
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Beks' friends aren't convinced by Sam Prince. Zeyno's home truths escalate into a blowout row. And how will Chuggs react when Livvy's spotted with another guy? (S30 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Olde Hitching Post: Gordon visits the historic Olde Hitching Post restaurant in Massachusetts. Tom bought the business for his daughter but refuses to let her run it. (S6 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Revisit: Gordon revisits Caf√© Hon in Baltimore, Chiarella's in Philadelphia, and Leone's in New Jersey, to find out whether the owners have taken his advice on board. (S6 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Levanti's: Gordon visits Pennsylvania, where he meets siblings whose inability to work together is risking their father's life savings at his Italian restaurant, Levanti's. (S6 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sam's Mediterranean Kabob Room: In California, Gordon visits Sam's Mediterranean Kabob Room, where he tries to mend relationships between the owner, his wife and their children. (S6 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Mill Street Bistro (Part 1/2): Gordon visits Ohio. The owner of the Mill Street Bistro claims to have the best menu between New York and LA. But the diners don't agree. (S6 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Platonic Permutation: At Thanksgiving, Sheldon and Amy hang out as friends at the aquarium, and Howard reluctantly agrees to volunteer at a soup kitchen. (S9 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Earworm Reverberation: Sheldon is driven to distraction when he can't get a familiar tune out of his head. Howard and Raj find out that their band has a fan. (S9 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Opening Night Excitation: Leonard, Howard and Raj have an extra ticket for the Star Wars movie premiere but can't decide who they should give it to. (S9 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Sales Call Sublimation: Penny gets more than she bargained for when Leonard meets a psychiatrist, while Sheldon and Raj make an astronomical discovery. (S9 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Empathy Optimization: The gang plan a Sheldon-free weekend in Las Vegas after coping with his constant demands, rudeness and ingratitude when he was ill. (S9 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Meemaw Materialization: Sheldon is thrilled when his beloved grandma 'Meemaw' comes to visit, but his excitement fades when she butts heads with Amy. (S9 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Great Christmas Bake Off 2023
E4Plus1.uk.description: Paul Hollywood and Prue Leith get festive with bakers of Christmas past Sophie, Dan, Amelia, Linda, George and Carole, and a performance from the Citizens of the World Choir.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Lisa's First Word: The family try to get Maggie to say her first word. But Homer's glad that she hasn't spoken yet, because all Lisa and Bart do is talk back to him. (S4 Ep10/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer's Triple Bypass: Homer has a heart attack while he's watching TV. The hospital says he needs a bypass, but Homer can't afford it. Of course, there's always Dr Nick... (S4 Ep11/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Marge vs the Monorail: When Springfield decides to install a monorail system, Homer is employed as the conductor. There's just one problem: he has no idea what he's doing. (S4 Ep12/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Selma's Choice: After Homer gets sick from a giant sandwich he's been eating for months, Selma steps in to take the kids to a new alcohol-based theme park. (S4 Ep13/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brother from the Same Planet: When Homer is late picking up Bart from a school football game, Bart gets a surrogate dad from an agency. (S4 Ep14/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox Festive Special
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers check out 2023's top Christmas telly, from The Real Full Monty: Jingle Bells to An Audience with Kylie, The 1% Club Christmas Special, Fur Babies, Men Up and Love Actually.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: This time, the Goggleboxers watch: Wildlife Rescue, Expedition X and Jamie's Air Fryer Meals. Also Baby Reindeer, Teen First Dates, The Circle and ITV News (Dogfather). (S23 Ep10) [SL]

Film4.uk.title: Last Night in Soho
Film4.uk.description: (2021) Edgar Wright's horror with Thomasin McKenzie, Anya Taylor-Joy and Matt Smith. A fashion student's transported back to Swinging-60s London. But nostalgia's not what it used to be...

Film4.uk.title: Once Upon a Time in Hollywood
Film4.uk.description: (2019) Quentin Tarantino's darkly comic drama set in 60s LA, starring Leonardo DiCaprio, Brad Pitt and Margot Robbie. A failing actor's world collides with the Manson Family.

Film4.uk.title: Against the Wind
Film4.uk.description: (1948) Spy thriller. Robert Beatty, Simone Signoret, Jack Warner and Gordon Jackson star as British-trained saboteurs sent to Second World War Belgium. But one of them is a traitor...

Film4.uk.title: The Caine Mutiny
Film4.uk.description: (1954) Oscar-nominated Humphrey Bogart, in one of his finest roles, stars in Edward Dmytryk's gripping drama as Captain Philip Queeg, in charge of a US Navy minesweeper during the war.

Film4.uk.title: Far from the Madding Crowd
Film4.uk.description: (1967) Julie Christie and Terence Stamp star in John Schlesinger's adaptation of Thomas Hardy's novel. Bathsheba is not short of suitors, but will marrying any of them lead to happiness?

Film4.uk.title: Hunter Killer
Film4.uk.description: (2018) Nautical action thriller. Gerard Butler stars as an unconventional submarine skipper sent to investigate the torpedoing of a US vessel. With Gary Oldman, Linda Cardellini and Common.

Film4.uk.title: Prey
Film4.uk.description: (2022) It's Predator, 1719 style. Amber Midthunder stars as a Comanche hunter who must save her tribe from an extraterrestrial threat in this action prequel. If it bleeds, you can kill it.

Film4.uk.title: The Running Man
Film4.uk.description: (1987) Classic 80s dystopian thriller, based on a Stephen King novel. Gadget-wielding murderers hunt an innocent man (Arnold Schwarzenegger) on a sick TV show.

Film4.uk.title: Sicario 2: Soldado
Film4.uk.description: (2018) Action sequel with Benicio Del Toro and Josh Brolin. Two operatives must create a gang war to stop Mexican drug cartels smuggling terrorists into the US.

Film4.uk.title: The Swimmer
